		"Name": "Amaris Fools: Somehow... Amaris Returned",
		"Details": "<b>THE END TIMES HAVE COME!</b>\r\n\r\n Apollo, [[DM.Factions[faction_RimWorldsRepublic],Rim Worlds Republic]]: Terrible news from the fringe tonight! Somehow, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStefanAmaris],Amaris]] has returned! He has reestablished his realm, the Rim Worlds Republic, and has openly declared his intent to conquer the worlds of the former Terran Hegemony! Quoth the man himself, \"You thought it was bad last time? You haven't seen anything yet, Inner Sphere dogs!\". Woe betide the Inner Sphere tonight as there is no [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAleksandrKerensky],Aleksandr Kerensky]] to save us this time!\r\n\r\n <b><color=#e51717>THIS EVENT TAKES A SHORT WHILE TO PROCESS, DO NOT PANIC YOUR GAME IS NOT FROZEN</color></b>",
