						"Details": "<b>THE SPECTER OF HISTORY!</b>\r\n\r\n For those who do not read their history, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStefanAmaris],Stefan Amaris]] is the oldest and greatest villain in Inner Sphere history. It was [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAmarisCivilWar],his actions]] that destroyed the first Star League, it was his actions that damned the Periphery to centuries of disrespect and irrelevance, and it was his actions that hurled mankind into the centuries-long dark age that was the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreSuccessionWars],Succession Wars]]. If someone doesn't rise up and stop him then the Inner Sphere is doomed to fall under his rule once more!\r\n\r\n <b><color=#e51717>THIS IS A TWO-PART EVENT, THE SECOND PART FIRES IN ONE DAY</color></b>",
